data.description: Beautifully updated energy efficient 5 bedroom 2 bath yellow octagon bungalow with a 2 car garage, and extra parking space and nice fenced private yard. The main floor features two oversized bedrooms with large closets, living room, formal dining room with hardwood floors throughout. The remodeled kitchen features new counter tops & backsplash, breakfast bar & walk in pantry. Recently updated bathroom with a Jacuzzi tub and a finished sun room/porch. The full finished basement features 2 large rooms with roomy closets, a full bath, wet bar, dinning room & a family room area! The 2nd floor master bedroom is enormous and has a large spacious walk in closet. This space could be used as recreation room, theater room, kids play/game room or an exercise room. The property also has newer windows, newer electrical, electrical panel, and new copper water lines. This beautiful home is ready for your family. Great neighborhood, with parks restaurants and communication at your door step and schools near by. There's nothing to do here but to move in! Your pickiest clients will be impressed!
